summary: I love to imagine how my 7 year old self would react to being brought into the current time to realize he’s going to see a world...
body:
I love to imagine how my 7 year old self would react to being brought into the current time to realize he’s going to see a world where something like Pokémon Go exists and there’s a live-action Pokémon movie with realistic looking Pokémon starring a talking Pikachu who’s a detective. This kind of stuff would have blown my mind… heck, as an adult I can hardly believe this stuff is out there.

I feel happy and excited for all the kids growing up with modern Pokémon.
